Visual Observers = Katherine Whitaker & Amanda Debich.  Begin cruise.  Leaving Port San Diego.  Heading on inshore, non-standard transect.  Observations off, working on observation platform set-up.  Transiting toward station 93/26.7.  Note that ship is transiting at ~ 11 knots, which is much faster than most other cruises.
